<section id="welcome" class="content-padding">
    <div>
        <aside>
            <!-- <img src="img/gus/hello.svg" alt="Gus saying hello"> -->
        </aside>

        <section id="welcome-text">
            <p class="intro">Welcome to owed  <span><s> version 3</s></span>, sorry, I mean owed+.</p>
            <p>Why is there a new owed app?</p>
            <p>To keep it brief: I wasn't able to successfully convert the old database to the new system. This means that if I had simply updated the existing app, there was a significant risk you could have lost some or all of your data.</p> 
            <p class="intro">Your experience is and always has been my top priority, so I didn't want to take that chance.</p>
            <p>I've invested considerable time and effort into this new app over the past 6 months. With all the hours spent designing and developing, I thought it would be fair to recoup some of that effort by charging a small fee ($1) for this version of the app.</p>
            <p class="intro">I really hope you enjoy this next chapter for the owed app!</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</section>